    "sub_sektor": "Apparel Manufacturing",
    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Golden Flower Tbk operates as an apparel manufacturing company in the United States of America, Indonesia, Hong Kong, Mexico, Canada, Korea, Panama, the Netherlands, China, and internationally. It operates through Ladies Blouse; Man Shirt; and Uniform, Accessories, and Others segments. The company offers light to medium weight woven apparel, including ladies' blouses, men's shirts, non-iron shirts, casual shirts, skirts, dresses, nightwear, and uniforms, etc. It also provides garment services, such as research and development, designing, cutting, sewing, washing, ironing, and finishing, as well as smoking, faggoting, and pleating services. In addition, the company engages in hospital, real estate, trading, and beauty clinic activities. It exports its products. The company was founded in 1958 and is based in Semarang, Indonesia. PT Golden Flower Tbk operates as a subsidiary of Pt Profashion Apparel.",
